  "time_ut": 1658382828,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db6\u0dd2\u0db3 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "During the swearing in of the President, the power goes out",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Secret Police has been handed over to investigate the power outage in the Parliament complex at the time of the swearing in of the President.",
        "The swearing-in ceremony of Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe as the 8th Executive President was scheduled to be broadcast live by Independent Television and broadcast by other television channels simultaneously.",
        "The live broadcast stopped after the President entered the Parliament complex on the red carpet.",
        "It was later reported that the live broadcast was stopped due to a power outage in the Parliament complex.",
        "In the event of a power outage in the Parliament complex, the generators are usually switched on automatically within two minutes and it is reported that the power was down for about ten minutes at the time of the swearing in of the President.",
        "Due to this reason, TV channels have not been able to cover live broadcasts."
      ],
